    <string name="settings_bank_auto_settle_title">Bank payment match hints (beta)</string>
    <string name="settings_bank_auto_settle_desc">Uses Android Notification Access to locally read bank/SMS app payment alerts. No READ_SMS permission, no cloud upload, and every settlement needs your confirmation.</string>
    <!-- Prominent disclosure (Play compliance) — Bank Notification Listener -->
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_title">Notification access</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_intro">Google requires a clear, in-app explanation before you use features that rely on notification access. Please read the sections below. This screen is shown only when you try to turn on Bank payment match hints.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_section_access">What we access</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_access_body">If you enable this beta feature and grant access in Android settings, HisabKitab Pro may receive titles and text from notifications posted by allowlisted banking and SMS/UPI apps on this device. We use that text only to detect a likely incoming payment amount and to look up a matching pending bill so we can show you a local suggestion. We do not read your SMS inbox (no READ_SMS), and we do not upload notification text to our servers.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_section_limits">What we do not do</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_limits_body">We do not store raw notification content in the database, send it to the cloud, or log it. Parsing runs on-device. Any settlement still requires your explicit confirmation inside the app.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_section_control">Your control</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_control_body">You can turn the feature off in Settings at any time, and you can revoke notification access for HisabKitab Pro in Android system settings. Until both are enabled, no bank match hints run.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_checkbox">I have read the above and agree to use Bank payment match hints under these terms.</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_continue">Continue</string>
    <string name="disclosure_bank_listener_privacy_link">View full privacy policy</string>
